params.name: data.dataset
params.description: The resource name of the Dataset used to train this Model.

params.name: data.gcs_source
params.description: The Google Cloud Storage uri of the unmanaged Dataset used to train this Model.

params.name: data.bigquery_source
params.description: The BigQuery table of the unmanaged Dataset used to train this Model.

params.name: data.data_format
params.description: Data format of the dataset, only applicable if the input is from Google Cloud Storage. The possible formats are: "tf-record" The source file is a TFRecord file. "csv" The source file is a CSV file. "jsonl" The source file is a JSONL file.

params.name: data.target_field
params.description: The target field name the model is to predict. This field will be excluded when doing Predict and (or) Explain for the training data.

params.name: data.logging_sampling_strategy
params.description: Strategy to sample data from Training Dataset. If not set, we process the whole dataset.
